msgstr "`options`（table，可选）：删除选项。支持："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:289
msgid ""
"`recursive` (boolean, optional): Whether to remove directories recursively. "
