msgstr "`recursive`（boolean，可选）：是否递归删除目录。默认值为 `false`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:289
msgid ""
"`missing_ok` (boolean, optional): Whether to ignore missing paths. Defaults "
"to `false`."
msgstr "`missing_ok`（boolean，可选）：路径不存在时是否忽略。默认值为 `false`。"

