msgstr "文件和符号链接无需 `recursive` 即可删除。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:298
msgid "Directories require `recursive = true` when they are not empty."
msgstr "目录在非空时需要设置 `recursive = true`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/worktrees/ptool/fresh-vale/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/fs.md:299
